### Action Types:
- **✅ ACCURATE**: File is correct and current
- **📝 UPDATE**: File needs content updates
- **🔄 REWRITE**: File needs complete rewrite
- **🗂️ RELOCATE**: File belongs in different location
- **🗑️ ARCHIVE**: File is obsolete and should be archived
- **🔗 REFERENCE**: File needs to reference accurate sources

